patriotism ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1966 japanese short film directed by yukio mishima . the english-language release was originally titled the rite of love and death and the french-language release was originally titled les rites de l'amour et de la mort . it is based on mishima 's short story patriotism ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) , published in 1961 .